Name: Mongoose Ritual Street (#2)
Short description: If you want baptism by air, here’s your ride. Not only does this bike clear big jumps with ease, its tough, chromoly frame feels nearly weightless when you’re off the ground! Add on 100mm of front suspension to cushion the drops and 3-piece cranks for that sweet barspin.

Name: Blackburn EX-1 Expedition Rack
Short description: Blackburn’s strongest rack is built for extended tours, off-road rides and long distance commutes. And it even holds a child seat for safe transport of your little one!

Name: Nirve Classic Single Speed Bike
Short description: From the local car show at the corner donut shop to the big time car meet in Carlisle, PA; the Classic and Kustom car culture is pure Americana. Drawing its influence from this popular lifestyle that fascinates enthusiasts worldwide, the Nirve Classic rolls into town with a vintage look and subtle appeal that’ll take you right back to the good ole’ days.

Name: Nirve Lahaina Single Speed Ladies
Short description: Nothing exemplifies the cruiser lifestyle better than a sunset ride along the waterfront with a balmy breeze blowing through your hair. The Nirve Lahaina features surf inspired graphics that are as much at home along the beaches as they are anywhere in the world. No matter where you live, you can claim your piece of paradise with this beautiful, casual cruiser.

Name: Schwinn Evolution IC Sleeveless Jersey
Short description: The pinnacle of Schwinn’s indoor cycling line, the Evolution IC Sleeveless Jersey is built to withstand countless hours of cardio-intense exercise on your favorite resistance unit!
Clothing Form: Skinny fit – cut closely to the body

Name: Shimano Ultegra FC-6500 53T
Short description: Smooth and nearly effortless, 9-speed shifting action that’s light, rigid and stiff.

Name: Prologue Photochromatic Multi-Lens
Short description: Break-away from the pack in these stylish sunglasses built for comfort, performance and easy viewing.

Name: Ascent Jet Set Head/Taillight Combo
Short description: See and be seen with highly visible front (white) and rear (red) LED lights!

Name: Northwave Women's Moon Road Shoe
Short description: Remember those comfy “moon boots” that Mom made you wear in the wintertime? They made you feel like you were walking on marshmallows! That’s why we couldn’t resist the Moon shoe from Northwave. Not only do these shoes have the technical features you need to go hard, they feel so luxuriously comfortable, you’ll never want to take them off!

Name: Forté CT100 Triathlon Shoe
Short description: Designed for lightning fast transitions and bike splits.
